{"tid":1083802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖沙嘴爭輸的士 20歲惡男牛肉刀怒斬23歲夜歸漢","createTime":"2019-03-30T01:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T11:09:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d7a7ea36a73b5dadbd3526d55b3ee4fddf974c","tid":1083802,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】兩名青年凌晨在尖沙嘴，懷疑因為爭乘的士先是口角繼而動武，期間，有人以雨傘及牛肉刀施襲。<br />\n現場為尖沙嘴金馬倫道與漆咸道南交界，雙方發生爭執後，一名23歲男子懷疑以手腳襲擊一名20歲男子，該名20歲男子亦懷疑以雨傘及刀襲擊對方，其後逃去。現場遺下斑斑血漬。<br />\n警員凌晨2時31分接報到場，在漆咸道南發現逃走的20歲男子倒臥地上，及檢獲一把雨傘及一把約55厘米長的牛肉刀，懷疑與案有關。<br />\n經初步調查，案件列在公眾地方打架，兩名男子涉案被捕，案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第七隊跟進。案中被斬的23歲男子面、背、腹傷，清醒被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理；20歲男子眼、口、頭受傷，昏迷被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理，其後回復清醒。<br />\n據悉，23歲男子在附近酒吧飲酒及擲飛標消遣後，截乘的士離開，登上的士一刻，上前爭乘的士的20歲男子，將隨身雨傘伸入車廂襲擊對方。<br />\n23歲男子於是下車還擊並搶去雨傘，糾纏期間，20歲男子拔出牛肉刀斬傷對方面臉部及手部。混亂間，揮刀男子的頭部及面部也受傷，並負傷逃去，最終倒臥地上。<br />\n據稱，涉嫌斬人的男子有案底，不排除事發時正爭趕往「劈友」，但在爭的士時生事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4ObOnErNoogr56xPpof_.Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190330a085133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4ObOnErNoogr56xPpof_.Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190330a085133.jpg&h=0d7adde5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%98%B4%E7%88%AD%E8%BC%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB-20%E6%AD%B2%E6%83%A1%E7%94%B7%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E5%88%80%E6%80%92%E6%96%AC23%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%9C%E6%AD%B8%E6%BC%A2-004900382.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B0%2596%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%2598%25B4%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB-20%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%2583%25A1%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2589%259B%25E8%2582%2589%25E5%2588%2580%25E6%2580%2592%25E6%2596%25AC23%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A4%259C%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E6%25BC%25A2-004900382.html&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7f3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=fb4685ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%98%B4%E7%88%AD%E8%BC%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB-20%E6%AD%B2%E6%83%A1%E7%94%B7%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E5%88%80%E6%80%92%E6%96%AC23%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%9C%E6%AD%B8%E6%BC%A2-004900382.html</a>"},{"pid":"8931a25c6bb111dfe4804239612abf7a4d4065ec","tid":1083802,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"咁巔"},{"pid":"b8615ea6edaa554e09f5235bcfbf896b671868f3","tid":1083802,"uid":90946,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:08:54.000Z","msg":"隨身都有牛肉刀<br />\n一定係做凍肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱愛工作到隨時斬肉"},{"pid":"c8f632f6c34585086a29c970d10023a4021e0c7b","tid":1083802,"uid":31094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:14:44.000Z","msg":"老牛在腰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a635b4be872d6a4a643190ccc83cf23515c5e9","tid":1083802,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:15:16.000Z","msg":"廢青<br />\n一定係ive公屋仔"},{"pid":"c46bf7881d826d60c47ffac9acedcee4d2a206ce","tid":1083802,"uid":3063,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"不排除事發時正爭趕往「劈友」，但在爭的士時生事。<br />\n<br />\n下次禮貌同人講<br />\n「喂 老友 我去緊劈友 john埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？」"},{"pid":"d210a022b26aab0c32e6a92654b8a60a9da2eedb","tid":1083802,"uid":68203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8f632f6c34585086a29c970d10023a4021e0c7b","tid":1083802,"uid":31094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:14:44.000Z","msg":"老牛在腰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"人擋殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\